    <!-- TextViews -->
    <string name="text_fact_human_description">After the outburst of the virus, certain humans were tasked with clearing the world of the infection, to that end, they employ the latest technology in weaponry and armoury.</string>
    <string name="text_fact_infected_description">The infected are hosts to a mysterious strain of virus, they seek to convert all living beings into tools for the High Overmind. An infected can gather different types of DNA sequences in order to improve themselves and defeat the Humans.</string>
    <string name="text_class_hum_soldier">Fitted with special armour and weapons, Soldiers will use any means necessary to fight the infection.</string>
    <string name="text_class_hum_scientist">Scientists use powerful tools allow them to support their fellow humans in combat by healing their wounds or prevent them from being infected.</string>
    <string name="text_class_inf_drone">Drones are melee infected. They are strongly built and can shrug off a few bullets while delivering powerful melee strikes.</string>
    <string name="text_class_inf_spitter">Spitters are ranged infected. They are weak to attacks but their poisonous darts allow them to deal considerable damage from a safe distance.</string>
    <string name="text_soldier_subclass">Engineer: Can deploy Ammo Crates and Repairing Machines.\nBlack-Ops: Bonus range unable to use heavy armour, may disappear from the radar.</string>
    <string name="text_scientist_subclass">Medic: Bonus healing, can set up Clinics (safehouses).\nInfection Control Officer: Access to ranged purging tools, more infection resistance.</string>
    <string name="text_drone_subclass">Shifter: Can appear as a human and is able to use some human weapons.\nHunter: More health, damage, damage mitigation. Ability to use Heavy DNA mutagens.</string>
    <string name="text_spitter_subclass">Queen Spitter: Bonus poison damage, can set up Hatcheries (safehouses).\nSovereign Mind: Boosts nearby infected stats and is able to deploy small dartlings.</string>
